    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Animal Kingdom 3, a hidden animal game where you collect pawprints and cameras while searching animals in fantastic locations! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049770/extras/c49f49ecb1ad7fabaed49f3cc6d65f26.poster.avif?t=1750102627\" width=562 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049770/extras/c49f49ecb1ad7fabaed49f3cc6d65f26.webm?t=1750102627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049770/extras/c49f49ecb1ad7fabaed49f3cc6d65f26.mp4?t=1750102627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With 3 game modes and trivias and jigsaw and swap puzzles between the chapters, Animal Kingdom 3 will provide hours of fun for Hidden Object fans in colorful jungles and other natural scenes and even underwater. Animal Kingdom 3 is waiting for you in this unique hidden object game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049770/extras/67066e3c5976abe4f809649c5605745e.poster.avif?t=1750102627\" width=562 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049770/extras/67066e3c5976abe4f809649c5605745e.webm?t=1750102627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049770/extras/67066e3c5976abe4f809649c5605745e.mp4?t=1750102627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Game Features</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replayable Hidden Animal scenes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animal puzzles along the way!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect photos and curiosities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cameras and pawprints to find!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Game Modes to choose from!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
